text: Gustavo Pacheco (born 12 May 1965) is an Argentine rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
